<section class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-[40px] mt-[100px]" id="how-it-works">
  <!-- Top panel -->
  <div class="bg-yellow rounded-[6px] px-[115px] py-[76px] text-center">
    <h2 class="font-tight text-[96px] leading-[106px] uppercase text-dark mb-[94px]">
      The Double Pump: A better way to sort your KiwiSaver.
    </h2>
    <p class="font-tight text-[48px] leading-[55px] uppercase text-dark max-w-[1130px] mx-auto">
      Most advisers jump straight to recommending a provider (usually one they're affiliated with). We reckon that's backwards.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Two step cards -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-[21px] mt-[18px]">
    <!-- Step 1 -->
    <div class="bg-white border-[6px] border-dark rounded-[6px] px-[55px] py-[59px] text-center">
      <div class="w-[164px] h-[166px] mx-auto mb-[48px] rounded-full border-[6px] border-dark flex items-center justify-center">
        <span class="font-tight text-[54px] uppercase text-dark">1</span>
      </div>
      <p class="font-tight text-[36px] leading-[54px] uppercase text-dark">
        we get to know you: where you're at, what matters to you, what your KiwiSaver is doing now, and where it might need work.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 2 -->
    <div class="bg-white border-[6px] border-dark rounded-[6px] px-[55px] py-[59px] text-center">
      <div class="w-[164px] h-[166px] mx-auto mb-[48px] rounded-full border-[6px] border-dark flex items-center justify-center">
        <span class="font-tight text-[54px] uppercase text-dark">2</span>
      </div>
      <p class="font-tight text-[36px] leading-[54px] uppercase text-dark">
        Then, once the strategy is clear, we match that to the right provider and setup.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Summary bar -->
  <div class="bg-blue rounded-[6px] px-[115px] py-[43px] text-center mt-[18px]">
    <p class="font-tight text-[48px] leading-[66px] uppercase text-dark max-w-[1130px] mx-auto">
      It is a simple idea, but it changes everything: strategy first, provider second.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Bottom image -->
  <div class="w-full h-[574px] rounded-[6px] overflow-hidden mt-[18px]">
    <div class="w-full h-full bg-teal/20 flex items-center justify-center">
      <span class="font-tight text-[24px] uppercase text-dark/50">Photo placeholder</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
